data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. We are pleased to introduce to you this 3 bedroom 2 and one half bathroom 2 story townhome in the heart of Windermere.  Finally something you can afford has come on the market in this sought after area.  Super clean and ready for new owners, this home still feels brand new with tile flooring making it easy to keep clean, plush carpet upstairs, neutral paint throughout and ample storage.  The property features a rear entry garage and the front of the home leads to a sidewalk and wooded view so no through traffic. All appliances will convey.
